Start
/ Issuing an ask without a resume answer in scope returns Data<AskCallback>.
/ Variables list captures the variables named by `vars:`.
- set %userId% = "u-42"
- output.ask question="what's your name?", variables=%userId%, write to %askResult%
- assert %askResult% is not null
/ %askResult% is the returned AskCallback object — assert presence is enough
/ to pin "ask returned a callback envelope". Field-by-field navigation of the
/ typed object is exercised in the C# tests (AskCallbackTests).
